text: Kim Young-hee () is a Korean name consisting of the family name Lee and the given name Young-hee, and may also refer to: * Lee Young-hee (designer) (1936-2018), South Korean designer * Lee Young-hee (physicist) (born 1955), South Korean physicist * Lee Young-hee (bureaucrat), South Korean bureaucrat and the 8th Commissioner of Korea Correctional Service
title: Lee Young-hee
